results.title: Irish Gaelic Gift Sign Live Well Laugh Often Love Much Rustic Vintage Shabby Chic Sign Extra Large
results.description:
Last Date For Orders For Guaranteed Christmas Delivery is 	
Sunday 9th December. Please order by this date. Gently distressed handmade Irish Gaelic wooden sign Gaelic "Mair Go Sona, Gairigh Go Minic, Graigh Alan" (Essence in translation is "Live well, laugh often love much!"

This is such a beautiful sign and would make a perfect gift.

This sign would grace any home or garden setting.

A great size for displaying on a door, above a door, amidst a wall display or gently resting on a shelf or mantle - the possibilities are endless.

Gently made to order using sustainably sourced or upcycled wood.

Available in a choice of gentle colours and all resting on a coal underlay - apart from the Vintage Cream which rests far more beautifully on a cocoa underlay.

made from:
All my signs are painted with great love and care - there is no cookie cutting process here - It's just me and a huge passion for creating great words on great signs!

All my signs are made from sustainably sourced or re-claimed wood.

No two pieces are ever the same - the wood grain, knots, notches, wood shakes will all vary and each tiny detail merely adds to the authenticity of each one I create.

Layers of paint, wax, artist quality acrylic letter work and seals are applied over a number of days - my pieces are created to be loved for a long time!

Sawtooth fixings are always attached ensuring that your sign is all ready for displaying as soon as you receive it.

This sign is suitable for indoor and outdoor use.

dimensions:
This piece measures approximately 71cm x 10cm x 2cm (28 inches x 4 inches x 3/4 of an inch)

Thank you so much for looking and please take a peep at my other signs - I can usually paint whatever words you require in any language and any style.


delivery:
Your order will be gently and carefully made over a number of days (sometimes up to 10 to 14 days to make  - due to layers of paint, wax and seals!) and will be sent out with a secure signed for and fully trackable courier delivery service.

results.title: Mini LIVE LOVE LAUGH Freestanding Resin Sign, Home Decor, Wedding, Top Table, Wedding Decoration. Choose Colour Or Custom Order!
results.description:
This beautiful, elegant mini freestanding LIVE LOVE LAUGH sign has been designed and hand-made by SMArtist.

This would make a wonderful, keepsake decoration or simply as a beautiful heartfelt gift to showcase in the home.

If you have a different colour in mind please feel free to message me and I will work with you to create yours with your chosen colour scheme. I can also use Silver, Copper and Gold leaf. Any other questions then please don't hesitate to send me a message.

Each word is a set size which are:

LIVE - 4 x 10.5 cm
LAUGH - 4 x 15.5 cm
LOVE - 4 x 12 cm

I use high-quality, UV resistant epoxy resin but I do recommend they aren't placed in direct sunlight as the heat could soften the resin. They can also be susceptible to scratches which can be polished out with care. They are wipe clean with a damp cloth only and shouldn't be left wet as they can dry with watermarks on. Please don't use any chemicals to clean this as they may react with the resin.
